# Course Viewer & Tracker Rules

Please read the instructions in [ai.md](file:///Users/maulik/Documents/GitHub/course-viewer/ai.md) before making edits or answering questions about this project.

- **Tech Stack**: Express.js (backend, port 3005), Vanilla JS SPA, CSS, and HTML5 (frontend).
